OL,3,CMurder investigation after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Londonderry
OL,6,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation following the death of a
OL,8,Fwoman in Londonderry.
OL,10,FOfficers attended a property in the
OL,11,FSummer Meadows Mews area on Saturday
OL,12,Fmorning where they located an injured
OL,13,Fwoman.
OL,15,FShe was subsequently taken to hospital
OL,16,Fwhere she has since died.
OL,18,FA 30-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
