OL,3,CMurder investigation after death of
OL,4,Cwoman in Londonderry
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with her family and
OL,7,Floved ones, who are left trying to
OL,8,Fcome to terms with this shocking
OL,9,Floss," a spokesperson for the PSNI
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Our enquiries are continuing, and I
OL,13,Fam appealing to anyone with
OL,14,Finformation, no matter how
OL,15,Finsignificant it may seem, to contact
OL,16,Four officers on 101."
